title: Path Finder - 6.5 [Intel/K]
description:
Version 6.5:

Fixed hanging issue some people experienced when launching Path Finder or opening Path Finder's application launcher. (OS X 10.9 Mavericks)
Fixed exceptions when saving image in the Image Editor.
Fixed exceptions some people experienced when using Text Editor.
Fixed drawers opening on start up (OS X 10.9 Mavericks)
Better synchronization of tags with Mavericks Finder and some other applications which use OpenMeta specification (such as Yep)

_______________________________________________

Path Finder is a file browser that combines the familiar Finder interface with the powerful utilities and innovative features.
